sequence:
The Bible teaches , “ Resist the devil and he will flee from you ” ( James 4:7 ) . It is also taught, “The Lord knows those who are seeking Him” . ( 1 John 3:12 ). We are called to do the same thing. “ The Lord loves a simple soul and the heart of a child ” . (Psalm 34 : 14 ) . This is why God calls us to trust in Christ. He calls us,

1) To believe that Jesus is my Saviour;

2)To believe that He is able to forgive me when I fail to forgive others.
